headline: Monolithic Power Systems (MPWR) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of power management chips maker Monolithic Power Systems (NASDAQ:MPWR) jumped 1.3% in the afternoon session after an analyst from Needham raised the company's stock price target by 25% to $1,025.
